<br>
Once I hit 51 I am sure my solo days are probably going to come to an end as the mobs will start hitting alot harder and it will greatly reduce the untility of my rune blade (and possibly my TOD).  I'm going to be upgrading to Fierce Heraldic armor as well and it will drop my Str down to 130's.  <br>
<br>
OK, now here are my questions.  <br>
<br>
How much of an impact is this str loss going to have on my damage output?  What's the minimum strength that is required for a shaman to buff you to 255?  Is it better to solo with the higher strength and keep my existing gear simply for that purpose?  I also duo with a cleric friend, what's the best gear setup for that? <br>
<br>
Any advice?<br>
<br>
