<br>
Anyway, you will want to max your AC, while keeping your regen.  Max hp are not as important, since you should not be fighting things that have a good chance at killing you.  If you have to use the ToD, you are probably fighting something too hard.  As for weapons, try for a 1:1 ratio two hander with a lower delay, 34/35ish would be great.  Until you break level 55 you won't get the ridiculous damage bonuses that make high delay two handers so good.  12/22 or better one handers with nothing slower than 22 delay in your main hand will do well for you also.  Buy the best weapons you can afford.  Bind wound is golden.  Max your skill asap, buy embalmer's skinning knives and/or anizok gauze press too.<br>
<br>
