<br>
I had a theory about lower AC with Str+fungi+high haste when leveling up to level 45.  It's simply this, with a str of over 200, decent weapons and haste, mobs before level 45 (approx.) don't hit you hard enough to compensate for your regen.  The high str, haste and weapons make for an extremely high DPS when soloing.  If they don't do enough damage outdamage the fungi tunic what's the point of a superhigh AC and HP?  I've found that there is almost no point as the supposed &quot;AC cap&quot; for low level mobs is extremely low.  <br>
